title: Ray Conniff - We Wish You A Merry Christmas (1962) (FLAC)
description:
Ray Conniff and the Ray Conniff Singers - We Wish You A Merry Christmas (1962)

FLAC

Originally released on vinyl, this CD was a 'digitally mastered analog recording' of the original.  Despite ripping this in highest quality, it has the sound of the old recording that it is.  I prefer it, as it brings back happy memories of many Christmas mornings, with this playing on the record player. Enjoy, may it call some fond memories to mind for you as well. 


1. Medley: Jolly Old St. Nicholas/The Little Drummer Boy: Jolly Old St. Nicholas / The Little Drummer Boy

3. Ring Christmas Bells

4. Medley: Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow!/Count Your ...: Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow! / Count Your Blessings (Instead Of Sheep) / We Wish You A Merry Christmas

5. The Twelve Days of Christmas

6. Medley: The First Noel/Hark! The Herald Angels Sing/O Come, All Ye ...: The First Noel / Hark! The Herald Angels Sing / O Come All Ye Faithful / We Wish You A Merry Christmas
